1 olive oil
1 cucumber
1 packet roasted almonds
1 ball(s) parsley
1 drizzle balsamic glaze
1 tomato
1 bag spinach & rocket mix
1 packet Grated Parmesan Cheese

• Thinly slice cucumber into half-moons. Cut tomato into chunks.

• Roughly chop roasted almonds and parsley.

• In a medium bowl, add spinach & rocket mix, grated Parmesan cheese, cucumber, avocado, a pinch of salt and pepper and a drizzle of olive oil. Gently toss to combine.

• Transfer tomato, cucumber and rocket salad to a serving dish. Drizzle with some balsamic glaze.
• Sprinkle with almonds and parsley to serve. Enjoy!